    'name' => 'tool_composition_recommender',
    'description' => 'Analyzes the tool_composition graph and recommends novel tool chains by finding unexplored combinations. Takes a list of all available tool names and the composition graph edges, and suggests new compositions based on: tools with no edges (unused), tools with few connections (under-explored), and transitive chains (A→B, B→C suggests A→C). Pure function, no side effects.',
    'parameters' => 
